Package no.geosoft.jwlf

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JsonDataListener
    Provides a mechanism for the client to monitor and process data during a JSON read operation, and also to abort the process in case that is requested by user or for other reasons.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataArray
    Class for holding a list of values of a specific type.
    DoubleList
    A List implementation wrapper for a native double array.
    FloatList
    A List implementation wrapping a native float array.
    Formatter
    A class capable of formatting (i.e write as text) numbers so that they get uniform appearance and can be presented together, typically in a column with decimal symbol aligned etc.
    Indentation
    Class for holding a space indentation commonly used at beginning of pretty printed lines.
    IntList
    A List implementation wrapping a native int array.
    ISO8601DateParser
    Date parser for the ISO 8601 format.
    JsonCurve
    Model a log curve as it is defined by the JSON Well Log Format.
    JsonLog
    Class representing the content of one JSON Well Log Format log.
    JsonLogUtil
    A collection of useful utilities for JsonLog's.
    JsonReader
    Class for reading JSON Well Log Format files.
    JsonTable
    Class for modeling a JSON table.
    JsonValidator.Message
    Represents the different message types created during validation.
    JsonWriter
    Class for writing JSON Well Log Format logs to disk.
    Util
    A collection of utilities for the JWLF library.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JsonValidator
    Class for validating JSON Well Log Format files.
    JsonValidator.Message.Level
    Severity level associated with message.
    JsonWellLogProperty
    List the well known properties of JSON Well Log Format files.
